Class Interval

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models.vars.histories.Interval
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConstrainedInterval

    public class Interval
extends java.lang.Object
    The class Interval implements a real value interval used in the definition of piecewise functions.

    Description

    Glass-box Invariants

     invariant       begin < end

    Black-box Invariants

     invariant       true        // no more invariant

    Created on : 2021-12-07

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
